commitResults.messageTitle: feat: Adapt MarkBind site for project
commitResults.messageBody:
- Added GitHub Actions write permissions for repo
- Updated site configs to match project fork:
	- Updated baseUrl in .github/workflows/docs.yml
	- Updated product name in docs/_markbind/layouts/default.md
	- Updated titlePrefix in docs/site.json

The index.md file was previously tailored for the addressbook3 project.
This commit updates the content to reflect new PatientSync project,
including the project name, description, and relevant links.

The changes include:
* Updating the project name to PatientSync
* Updating the project description

This update is necessary to provide accurate and relevant information
about the PatientSync project on the main page of the documentation.

Give acknowledgements that this project is based on the
AddressBook-Level3 project created by the SE-EDU intiative

commitResults.messageTitle: Beautify and Add Descriptions for Project Links
commitResults.messageBody:
Improve the presentation of project links by using a table format.
Also provide descriptions for each link to give users more context.
This enhances readability and provides users with quick insights
into the purpose of each link.

These changes aim to make navigating the project resources
easier for users and developers alike.
V1.1 acknowledgement + Project Links table in Home Page
